name: Caroline
description:
Barefoot Sandal - Caroline 
Color: Coral 
Size: One size fits most adults (Contact me for smaller sized feet)
Sold as a pair.

Stranded using Stretch Magic. Therefore, is stretchable to an extent. Made with various glass beads and stone accent beads.

Wear them for any occasion ranging from a day on the beach to a night on the town. Can be worn alone or with with shoes. They make any foot look prettier.
